point_one.title: <:TheCubeTeam:924763912992329821> **__Privacy Policy__**
point_one.description: >>> The purpose of Cubed is not just to have fun or entertain you, Cubed seeks to take your community to the next level through the information collected throughout its use, for this reason we present a list of things that we want to clarify, in this way we seek that you feel comfortable with the information that is collected through Cubed, remember that once Cubed is inside the server, the Privacy Policy will take effect.

point_two.title: <a:Arrow:933834822739193897> **Stored Data**
point_two.description: >>> Some of the commands, when executed, require certain information. Therefore, the User must provide the information required for Cubed to continue with the execution of said command, for this Cubed would obtain the information from the Server such as: **Server Name**, **Server Id**, **Channel Id**, and also Cubed may obtain the following information: **Server Owner**, **Server Owner Id**, **Member IDs**.

point_three.title: <a:Arrow:933834822739193897> **Message Content**
point_three.description: >>> Cubed does not store messages in its **Database** or other external site, instead Cubed will be able to access the content of the message and due to this, it is possible to Moderate your server like this Please note that Cubed only caches **Deleted Messages** and **Edited Messages** for 1 hour.
